name: Spirit Bay
description:
This oasis is only accessible through a complicated series of portals that must be entered and exited in a specific order. Those who find their way here do so with the intention of never leaving, to pass on to the other side. Huge gods, the size of buildings inhabit the bay, looking for any signs of human life. 

Digital illustration created in procreate. 2292px X 1714px. 132 DPI
